<item>
            <title>[LU-4369] configure option &quot;--without-ldiskfs&quot; does not build</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4369</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Not sure when this option stopped working in master, but I think it was fairly recently.  I&apos;ve tried --without-ldiskfs and --disable-ldiskfs on the ./configure command line.  &apos;make rpms&apos; after either one fails.  Seems to be looking for ldiskfs.ko and osd-ldiskfs.ko files to write into some rpm in spite of the configure options.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="22405">LU-4369</key>
